This analysis was compromised by several critical errors in the computational pipeline, impacting the validity of key research hypotheses.
*   ‚ùå **PSCI Calculation Failure**: The primary `Populist Strategic Contradiction Index (PSCI)` failed to compute due to a code-level error [11]. This prevents assessment of overall strategic contradiction.
*   ‚ùå **ANOVA Test Failures**: All Analysis of Variance (ANOVA) tasks (`task_04`, `task_05`, `task_08`) failed due to missing data columns. This makes it impossible to statistically test for differences across time or speech context (Hypotheses H1, H2, H5).

